  30 Jun 2012; Daniel Scharrer <dscharrer@gentoo.org> files/install-cd,
  files/install-gog, files/install-verify:
  Disable the innoextract progress bar and ignore missing .pdf files

  21 Apr 2012; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org> files/install-verify:
  Don't fail if both speech.pak and speech_default.pak exist in the source data

  19 Apr 2012; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org> files/install-cd,
  files/install-copy, files/install-gog, files/install-verify:
  Update install scripts from Arx Libertatis: Make sure the CWD is valid before
  calling find or it might fail in a sandboxed environment.

  19 Apr 2012; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org> +files/install-verify,
  -files/install-common, files/install-cd, files/install-copy,
  files/install-gog:
  Update install scripts from Arx Libertatis: support both variants of data.pak
  for all localisations.

  14 Apr 2012; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-fatalis-data-1.21.ebuild, +files/install-common, -files/data-de.md5,
