  -files/data-it.md5, -files/data-ru.md5, files/install-cd, files/install-copy,
  files/install-gog:
  Update install scripts from Arx Libertatis.

  13 Apr 2012; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org> +files/data-it.md5,
  files/install-cd, files/install-copy:
  Add support for italian data files.

  09 Apr 2012; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org> files/install-cd,
  files/install-copy:
  Support .pak files with a _default suffix.

  08 Apr 2012; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org> files/install-cd,
